36#include "windlocl.h"
37
38#include <stdlib.h>
39
40#include "combining_table.h"
41
42static int
43translation_cmp(const void *key, const void *data)
44{
45 const struct translation *t1 = (const struct translation *)key;
46 const struct translation *t2 = (const struct translation *)data;
47
48 return t1->key - t2->key;
49}
50
51int
52_wind_combining_class(uint32_t code_point)
53{
54 struct translation ts = {code_point, 0};
55 void *s = bsearch(&ts, _wind_combining_table, _wind_combining_table_size,
56 sizeof(_wind_combining_table[0]),
57 translation_cmp);
58 if (s != NULL) {
59 const struct translation *t = (const struct translation *)s;
60 return t->combining_class;
61 } else {
62 return 0;
63 }
64}
